00:09:23.690 --> 00:09:25.482
So I have a static
observer, so an observer

00:09:25.482 --> 00:09:28.330
who is not moving in space.

00:09:28.330 --> 00:09:29.830
They're only moving
through time.

00:09:29.830 --> 00:09:32.823
And I need to normalize
