00:18:46.547 --> 00:18:47.770
of the way this is behaving.

00:18:47.770 --> 00:18:49.690
The key thing which
I want to emphasize

00:18:49.690 --> 00:18:57.895
is that as r goes to 2GM,
what we see is that--

00:18:57.895 --> 00:18:59.270
well, let's just
